---
/**
 * ArticleSubsection — inner content block inside an ArticleSection.
 * Mirrors Figma layer "Sub Section" (node 2444:1759 / 2564:3234).
 *
 * Thin wrapper around <div class="article-subsection"> — carries the 12-col
 * canvas grid and all column-placement rules (prose centered in col 4–9 at xl,
 * figures col 3–10 at xl). Authors write regular MDX inside (H2, paragraphs,
 * figures, callouts, post-meta, etc.) and children drop onto the grid.
 *
 * No props — all variation comes from children.
 */
---

<div class="article-subsection">
  <slot />
</div>
